        </p>
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5">
          However, Mexican prosecution of serving politicians remains minimal due to constitutional protections. The precedent of arresting officials while in office, such as the <a style="text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid  #4D3060; color: black;" href="https://link.presidentialsummary.com/ps-12-jun-25-spotlight-h1-2-2020-arrest?source=website" target="_blank">2020 arrest</a> of former Defense Secretary, has strained US-Mexico relations. </p>
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;filter:blur(5px);">
